A police VIP protection unit officer who allegedly shot dead a 17-year-old Dale College pupil is under investigation by the police s watchdog body. The pupil, Anathi Qabisisa, was shot during the school s 156th reunion celebrations on May 15.King William s Town police spokeswoman Captain Siphokazi Mawisa confirmed that a murder docket had been handed over to the Independent Police Investigative Directorate (Ipid).For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions